                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2002-12-05</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>Apart from being clear and well-written, this book is also the sum of all the knowledge of the Mason community, written by two of the developers of Mason themselves.<BR>If you already use Mason, it's a must have.<BR>If you are new to Mason, try it first (it isn't difficult at all), then read the book.<BR>From my point of view this is an excellent technical book.</span>
                  
              
